{"tid":2061750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍絲懲教殺人早有前科]2002年小欖精神病治療中心曾用毒藥殺害囚犯","createTime":"2020-06-12T15:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T23:38:16.000Z","uid":26770,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"37d611536a17b466bd62cbcf01130ca60deb1e26","tid":2061750,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:17:40.000Z","msg":"1)立會聲稱：有意投訴也會被打針<br />\n三釋囚爆懵仔針黑幕<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20021106/2929931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20021106%2F2929931&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=14186549\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20021106%2F2929931&h=3ed296cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20021106/2929931</a><br />\n<br />\n2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr02-03/chinese/panels/se/papers/se0123cb2-947-01-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr02-03%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fse%2Fpapers%2Fse0123cb2-947-01-c.pdf&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=f3bb84d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr02-03/chinese/panels/se/papers/se0123cb2-947-01-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1)囚犯張志堅被注射過量「懵仔針」致死事件<br />\n死者張志堅因得罪精神病治療中心館方<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遭注射過量藥處死</span><br />\n而唔少曾嘗試投訴或得罪管方的人都曾遭捉去打「懵仔針」<br />\n<br />\n2)故意用高量藥物<ins>殺人立威</ins>,令囚犯係死亡威脅下聽話係香港懲教一直的手法<br />\n大家查下定時定侯就有一批囚犯離奇死亡/重傷,<ins>明顯有計劃有組織的</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後就只有幾頁無撚聊的立法會文書, 殺人者不受追責</span>"},{"pid":"7a4043f2f8648877a93f4556fd8af120e8751695","tid":2061750,"uid":151074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:21:58.000Z","msg":"小欖Death Camp"},{"pid":"92a058e63c888bf64211f7551643ce36be71b8a5","tid":2061750,"uid":26770,"li